msgid "Biological Age"
msgstr "Edad Biológica"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:14
msgid "How it's calculated"
msgstr "Cómo se calcula"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:16
msgid "Hide details"
msgstr "Ocultar detalles"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:17
msgid "See the 9 markers"
msgstr "Ver los 9 marcadores"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:20
msgid ""
"We use <strong>PhenoAge</strong> (Levine et al., 2018), a scientifically "
"validated algorithm that estimates your biological age by combining your "
"chronological age with 9 biomarkers from your blood test. Each marker "
"reflects the state of a different system in your body:"
msgstr ""
"Usamos <strong>PhenoAge</strong> (Levine et al., 2018), un algoritmo "
"científicamente validado que estima tu edad biológica combinando tu edad "
"cronológica con 9 biomarcadores de tu analítica de sangre. Cada marcador "
"refleja el estado de un sistema diferente de tu cuerpo:"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:41
msgid "Albumin"
msgstr "Albúmina"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:41
msgid "hepatic protein."
msgstr "proteína hepática."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:41
msgid "Decreases with aging."
msgstr "Disminuye con el envejecimiento."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:42
msgid "Creatinine"
msgstr "Creatinina"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:42
msgid "kidney function."
msgstr "función renal."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:42
msgid "Tends to rise with age."
msgstr "Tiende a subir con la edad."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:43
msgid "Glucose"
msgstr "Glucosa"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:43
msgid "energy metabolism."
msgstr "metabolismo energético."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:43
msgid "Rises with aging and sedentary lifestyle."
msgstr "Sube con el envejecimiento y el sedentarismo."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:44
msgid "CRP"
msgstr "PCR"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:44
msgid "systemic inflammation."
msgstr "inflamación sistémica."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:44
msgid "High CRP ages the result further."
msgstr "Una PCR alta envejece más el resultado."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:45
msgid "MCV"
msgstr "VCM"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:45
msgid "red blood cell size."
msgstr "tamaño de los glóbulos rojos."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:45
msgid "Changes with age and diet."
msgstr "Cambia con la edad y la dieta."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:46
msgid "RDW"
msgstr "ADE"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:46
msgid "erythrocyte variability."
msgstr "variabilidad eritrocitaria."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:46
msgid "Highest weight in calculation; elevated indicates cellular stress."
msgstr "Mayor peso en el cálculo; elevado indica estrés celular."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:47
msgid "Alkaline Phosphatase"
msgstr "Fosfatasa Alcalina"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:47
msgid "bone and liver status."
msgstr "estado óseo y hepático."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:47
msgid "Rises with tissue damage and age."
msgstr "Sube con el daño tisular y la edad."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:48
msgid "WBC"
msgstr "Leucocitos"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:48
msgid "immune system."
msgstr "sistema inmune."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:48
msgid "Altered by aging."
msgstr "Alterado por el envejecimiento."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:49
#, python-format
msgid "%% Lymphocytes"
msgstr "%% Linfocitos"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:49
msgid "adaptive immune response."
msgstr "respuesta inmune adaptativa."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:49
msgid "Decreases with age (immunosenescence)."
msgstr "Disminuye con la edad (inmunosenescencia)."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:53
msgid ""
"The algorithm combines these 9 values using a formula derived from more than "
"11,000 people in the NHANES population study. The result is an "
"<strong>estimated biological age</strong>: if it is lower than your real "
"age, your body is functioning better than expected; if it is higher, there "
"is room for improvement."
msgstr ""
"El algoritmo combina estos 9 valores con una fórmula derivada de más de "
"11.000 personas del estudio poblacional NHANES. El resultado es una "
"<strong>edad biológica estimada</strong>: si es menor que tu edad real, tu "
"cuerpo funciona mejor de lo esperado; si es mayor, hay margen de mejora."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:57
msgid ""
"⚠️ This estimate is <strong>indicative and educational</strong>, not a "
"medical diagnosis. A single value may be affected by recent infections, "
"medication or the time of blood draw. Its greatest utility is "
"<strong>tracking over time</strong>."
msgstr ""
"⚠️ Esta estimación es <strong>orientativa y educativa</strong>, no un "
"diagnóstico médico. Un valor puntual puede verse afectado por infecciones "
"recientes, medicación o el momento de la extracción. Su mayor utilidad es el "
"<strong>seguimiento a lo largo del tiempo</strong>."

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:67
msgid "Biological age evolution"
msgstr "Evolución de la edad biológica"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:98
msgid "years younger"
msgstr "años más joven"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:98
msgid "years older"
msgstr "años mayor"

#: labs/templates/labs/phenoage/history.html:112
msgid "Not enough data yet to calculate your biological age."
msgstr "Aún no hay suficientes datos para calcular tu edad biológica."

